  "descriptions": [
    {
      "text": "幻獣旅団は、Créa-Tech Inc.が開発した戦略ゲームです。あなたは、豚の王国を征服することを決意した人間の軍を指揮します。弓兵、騎士、魔法使いなど、さまざまなタイプのユニットが登場します。戦略と鋭い判断力が、あなたの部隊を勝利へと導くために必要です…。",
      "lang": "ja",
      "source": "romu"
    },
    {
      "text": "Genjuu Ryodan is a Strategy game, developed by Crea-Tech and published by Axela, which was released in Japan in 1998.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb"
    },
    {
      "text": "It takes place in the fictional world of Vulcandra, where monsters and humans once lived in harmony together. However, things get serious after the antagonist Skullkaiser and his hellish army breaks out of the big volcano Nifelgap. The kingdom of Belborg uses the state of chaos over Volcandra to declare themselves to be the doubtful saviors of humanity and subjugate numerous smaller kingdoms. The player takes control of the “peaceful” kingdom of Earthring, which are on the edge of their defeat against Belborg.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "igdb_storyline"
    }
  ],
